# Input

```scss
$foo:(property1:(),// comment 1
// comment 2

property2:1,/** comment 1 */
/* comment 2 */
property3:2);

$line:(// keep
key:(inner:value,),);

```


# Formatted

```scss
$foo: (
	property1: (),
	// comment 1
	// comment 2
	property2: 1,
	/** comment 1 */ /* comment 2 */ property3: 2,
);

$line: (
	// keep
	key: (
			inner: value,
		)
);

```
